dct_description_sm: Department of the Interior, U.S. Geological Survey.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
Title in upper right corner: Texas, San Antonio quadrangle; at head of map: Topography.
"Topography by W. H. Herron, J. F. Mc.Beth, E. R. Bartlett, and Fred Mc.Laughlin. Triangulation by A. H. Thompson and T. M. Bannon."; surveyed in 1901-1903.
On verso: The camps around San Antonio / by L. W. Stephenson. -- 7 columns : ill., map.
